    "epigenetic_rescue": [
      "Individuals with VDR mutations must maintain much higher optimal blood levels (60-80 ng/mL) of Vitamin D3 to force the sluggish receptors into action.",
      "Mandatory co-supplementation with NUT_MAGNESIUM_001 (Magnesium is required to activate the VDR itself)."
